# Interconnections and additional details
# =============================================================================

# Link agents to resources they manage
noria-org:NetworkOperationsCenter noria:agentManagesResource noria-resource:Router_Core_01 .
noria-org:ApplicationSupport noria:agentManagesResource noria-resource:App_Server_05 .

# Link resources to applications they support
noria-resource:Router_Core_01 noria:resourceForApplication noria-app:Monitoring_Platform .
noria-resource:App_Server_05 noria:resourceForApplication noria-app:CRM_System .

